title: I Built an iOS App in 27 minutes Using this AI Tool Nobody Knows (Vibe Code App Review)

In this product teardown, I try the Vibe Code app from Riley Brown's company that let's you build iOS apps right on your phone. No coding, no desk, just custom apps built from scratch from wherever you are.

I wanted to find out what the product was like, how well it builds apps, if you can sell them on the app store, and how good it was in translating my ideas to actual apps.

Try vibe code here: https://www.vibecodeapp.com

Key points:

- I create my idea in Vibe Code and test the first version of my app

- I tweak my idea and make changes, exploring how bugs are handled and how Vibe Code translates my ideas to code

- I get the AI functionality working, and create my own strategic advisor app in Vibe Code that translates my voice notes into highly leveraged business actions

- I explore ways I could publish the app on the app store and what direction the app should take
